%N A395708 Expansion of g^4*(4*g-3)/(3-2*g)^4, where g = 1+x*g^3 is the g.f. of A001764.
%F A395708 a(n) = (n+1) * A062236(n+1).
%F A395708 G.f.: (Sum_{k>=0} (6*k+1)/(3*k+1) * binomial(3*k+1,k) * x^k) * (Sum_{k>=0} binomial(3*k,k) * x^k)^3.
%F A395708 Sum_{k>=1} a(k-1) * x^k/k^2 = (1/2) * log( Sum_{k>=0} binomial(3*k-1,k) * x^k ).
%F A395708 a(n) = (n+1) * Sum_{k=0..n} binomial(3*k+2+l,k) * binomial(3*n-3*k-l,n-k) for every real number l.
%F A395708 a(n) = (n+1) * Sum_{k=0..n} 2^(n-k) * binomial(3*n+3,k).
%F A395708 a(n) = (n+1) * Sum_{k=0..n} 3^(n-k) * binomial(2*n+k+2,k).
%o A395708 (PARI) a(n) = (n+1)*sum(k=0, n, 2^(n-k)*binomial(3*n+3, k));
